Interface DocumentRevisionRepository

All Superinterfaces:
org.springframework.data.repository.CrudRepository<DocumentRevision,Long>, org.springframework.data.jpa.repository.JpaRepository<DocumentRevision,Long>, org.springframework.data.jpa.repository.JpaSpecificationExecutor<DocumentRevision>, org.springframework.data.repository.ListCrudRepository<DocumentRevision,Long>, org.springframework.data.repository.ListPagingAndSortingRepository<DocumentRevision,Long>, org.springframework.data.repository.PagingAndSortingRepository<DocumentRevision,Long>, org.springframework.data.repository.query.QueryByExampleExecutor<DocumentRevision>, org.springframework.data.repository.Repository<DocumentRevision,Long>
@Repository public interface DocumentRevisionRepository extends org.springframework.data.jpa.repository.JpaRepository<DocumentRevision,Long>, org.springframework.data.jpa.repository.JpaSpecificationExecutor<DocumentRevision>
The DocumentRevisionRepository interface provides access to document revision-related data stored in the database.
